<br />
Jades I do like your idea of the Chaos Volley Dealing damage every 5 seconds but is it going to do that on its own or do we have to recast it... i'm not sure if i understand.  The thing is we will have every fight we start off with chaos volley and then we start casting other arcan spells.... welll then what happens next?? we just keep using Taqmirs,mimic, SG and CV will automatically do something every 5  seconds??  <br />
<br />
