<br />
And to be honest i feel like if we are locked into having to first cast CV in the beginning of the fight  i feel like it would be as illusive has said previously in posts that it would be the game dictating how we have to play our characters .  We will lose the freedom to do our DPS in other ways except one.  Other melee classes have the ability to crit and do chains and other combos and do DPS in different ways... I feel if we have to cast CV and then use other arcane spells to ramp it up... then we are stuck using CV, TAQ, MIMIC and SG all the time and it will make our other spells almost useless as they alone wont be able to compare to the DPS (unless they are going to go an incredible hike in damage also).<br />
