                  <u><font color="Cyan">Simple Suggestion</font></u><br />
<br />
Hey guys,  I don't know about many of you, but I really hate this forum tag stuff.  Is there anyway we as a Sorcerer community can get a bit more organized and sit down one night during the week on an IRC network or even a ventrilo network so we can get a better feeling about other members of the community on what their ideas are.  <br />
<br />
Right now I read one post go to make a comment about it and before I finish typing some one else has posted a big long book that I have to read than filter into what I was going to type.  As a raid leader I try to press the fact better communication is the key.  However we can get our points across and get a better understand were others will come from usually decreases drama.
                  
		</div>
		<!-- / message -->
	
		
		
		
		
		
	
	</td>
</tr>
<tr>
